##  Rekomendasi untuk Project EWI

Untuk project KPI EWI ini, jika ada masalah cache setelah update backend:

### **Quick Clean** (Paling Sering Dipakai):
```bash
# 1. Hapus __pycache__
Get-ChildItem -Recurse -Directory -Filter __pycache__ | Remove-Item -Recurse -Force

# 2. Restart Flask server
# Ctrl+C untuk stop
python app.py  # Start lagi
```

### **Deep Clean** (Jika Ada Masalah Besar):
```bash
# 1. Hapus __pycache__
Get-ChildItem -Recurse -Directory -Filter __pycache__ | Remove-Item -Recurse -Force

# 2. Hapus .venv dan install ulang (jika perlu)
Remove-Item -Recurse -Force .venv
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 3. Restart Flask
python app.py
```

---

##  Perbandingan Flutter vs Python

| Flutter | Python/Flask |
|---------|--------------|
| `flutter clean` | Hapus `__pycache__` |
| `flutter pub get` | `pip install -r requirements.txt` |
| `flutter run` | `python app.py` |
| Hot reload | Flask debug mode auto-reload |
| Build artifacts (`build/`) | `__pycache__`, `.pyc` |

